Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The energy of the beetles is positive. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. The beetles put out, let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The stones put out, let it bleed. That gives you a little hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have a whole generation concerned with killing guns on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They watch homicides, and they play killer games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They listen to rock music, and then you throw in drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So with the drugs, you're in a very suggestible hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens to these people is they become dominated by negative energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Their consciousness becomes dominated by the attractor energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can demonstrate this over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rise of street crime and criminal activity by adolescents,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the public is well advised to be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are programmed negative killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was one on TV the other night who shot another one of his young classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked why he did it, he said he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't know. He's in an unconscious hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He just pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as he does on combat, you know, the same as the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So the negative lyrics of this kind of music are pounded into your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in a highly suggestible hypnotic state in which your negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your energy fields are already negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why it's so complicated by the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real tragedy of modern society,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a whole generation of youth is being wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole generation is being wiped out by computer games, heavy metal rock, every cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've tested every kind of music, and of course classical music makes you go strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,country western makes you go strong, reggae, soft rock makes you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a study, which I mentioned in the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at Sedona Villa, cocaine addicts after discharge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,those who continued to listen to heavy metal rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the recovery rate was zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, nobody recovered if they continued to hang out in that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the music itself? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the music itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the energy that accompanies that music.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is a great research tool for parapsychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The current techniques used in parapsychology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to either prove or disprove a phenomena are equally fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove or disprove the presence of other invisible entities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by using infrared or Geiger counters or ultraviolet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, those are all in a different domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove the immaterial in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,by using techniques that are suitable for the material universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy who makes a living running around
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,knocking parapsychology, the great Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the great Randy is positive. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the great Randy is negative. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He emanates a very negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because his motivation is to disprove the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the gross dedication to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it's based on a false premise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you can imitate a phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore you've negated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's obviously fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imitate any real phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but by imitating it doesn't disprove
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the real phenomena actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought that parapsychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because a lot of people are interested in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,its use in politics and government,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, is extremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test out the government's present policy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the president's war on drugs is positive. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's effective. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's political BS. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's political BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The war on drugs, the energy of it is over 160. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 150. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The war on drugs calibrates at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's see what we would need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to effectively affect the war on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The government's program would have to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,over 350. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 360. 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to have a program,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,government program funded program,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrates at 350 to handle the drug problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot handle a drug problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with a program that calibrates only at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used in politics, it's used in sociology,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's used in politics, are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought sort of an interesting one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called false memory syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more lawsuits are being brought against therapists
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who inculcate false memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just check out this whole false memory syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These memories of our early childhood sexual abuse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that are foggy and really only come to life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,via the therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,those are real memories, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are false over 60% of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,70% of the time, 80% of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that these repressed memories
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of childhood sexual abuse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are false about 80% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One out of five, it actually happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,four out of five, it's false.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology demonstrates this very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of innocent people have been accused,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,lives have been destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,families have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody forgets that Freud discovered that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at the beginning of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All his female patients laying down on the couch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere along the analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they would remember early childhood incestuous fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, Freud was flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought, how can all these fathers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,be molesting all these little girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just statistically, from a criminologic viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the percentage of the population
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that does this kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is very, very small, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he found that these were
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious fantasies, incestuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, this was part of the Oedipal complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Society has gone into repression
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and unconsciousness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the return of the repressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and now tries to make it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can be compensated for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Victimhood really pays in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the use of kinesiology can be very, very useful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in psychological research in general,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as theory goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and as far as an individual case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think now of an individual case
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of a patient I'm treating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The sexual abuse which took place in her childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The case I'm thinking about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the childhood sexual abuse was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one that was suggested to a patient of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by a therapist, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea here, the way the scenario goes is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything before I was eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, the therapist figures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, there must have been a lot of sexual abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These are people who have not been trained
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in psychoanalytic theory, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Childhood amnesia is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal people don't remember what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,up until they were five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the resolution of the edible complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in my view of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,current pop psychology does not explain phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of current pop psychology
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,having to do with this repressed memory
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and all this kind of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's supposed to contribute to eating disorders,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bulimia, and all these kind of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is scientifically accurate, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Freudian theory is much closer to the truth about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Freudian theory is a lot closer to the truth about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the false memory syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mode in which I've been using it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and describing it in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially that field called spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just test out some of the,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because this affects the lives of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a fellow right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to hold that over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's energy is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About 540 is the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the book he wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson, the founder of AA,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the language of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 500s is the language of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So people who were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you calibrate what was their level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when they came into this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,people who calibrated in the 500s
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are preoccupied with love and its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is love, how to define love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between spiritual love and personal love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how to let go of attachments,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and love, you might say, universally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's, I mentioned before, A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles is very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see why in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 590, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 610, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 599, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,600.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,620.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,600.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates approximately at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook in A Course in Miracles calibrates at 600, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook calibrates over 600, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook is a little less useful than the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's interesting about this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is that 600 is the level at which form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to disappear into formless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And 600 is also exactly the level of kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason people have used kinesiology for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will still say, I don't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it is that level at which
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego is not familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego dominates the levels below 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego does not dominate from 600 on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a different aspect of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual ego dominates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ego is not used to working
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600 or over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything 600 or over,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so the scientific people who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,poo-poo anything that is not within
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical, mechanical, measurable domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,do so because their level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as we've seen, goes up to 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't comprehend things in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't get essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't get significance beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the measurable domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there was a recent article in Science
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that said something about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no reality except
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that which can be measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the name of the article was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is Measurement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, reality is measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is a level at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which we all consider
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,worth dying for,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and people in the 500s and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with the non-measurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These are people willing to die for love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for the welfare of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For spiritual principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are not measurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't weigh them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even exist anywhere in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's move up the people then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one bit even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the Bhagavad Gita,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,revered of ancient Hindu wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it calibrates over 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,750,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,740,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,740.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,these are very interesting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They are enlightened gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Typically with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachings of Jesus, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Buddha is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,after 2000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,people who didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what it meant in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,repeated it to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what it meant in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And nobody really has any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what Jesus Christ said, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you put together everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Bible and the New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that Jesus Christ said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't cover more than a few pages, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, in those years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he gave all kinds of lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These are interesting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Nisargadatta Maharaj,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who only died in the 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's an enlightened guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of his book is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,well, what he spoke about was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he identified with awareness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very high level consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisargadatta Maharaj is 700, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 750, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,710,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,720,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,730,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the low 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another guru of recent vintage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a saint,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sri Ramana Maharshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He died about 1958.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just ask with this whole bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of this spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,720,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,730,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,740,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,750,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the low 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that which the world calls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,really pure spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,real gurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not false ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out another supposed guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because one use of this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is to tell the false from the true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the organ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajneesh has a positive energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the other one in India
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that stresses out our beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy is positive, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a lot of the ones that people in the new age,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, go ooh and ahh over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty there is that the error,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual error,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is on such a level,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it's beyond the awareness of the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the naive spiritual student,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,his consciousness goes up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The guru goes up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he seems impressive to the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the guru himself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is out because his integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is out on a level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that is beyond the student's capacity to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can see where that guru is out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is somebody who himself has been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to that level and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who tells you they're higher than Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is a false guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no being on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that has ever been higher than Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been a being on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,whose consciousness was higher than that of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who claims that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims it all the time to various people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer claims to be higher than Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lucifer that thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you see demonstration of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,money, collections of automobiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and riches, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi lived a life of absolute simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even bother with a plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He ate off a leaf in native style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that you're as high or higher than Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is obviously fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha calibrates over 990,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,over 1,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,over 1,100.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna calibrates about 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The great avatar is calibrated at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The human body is capable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of coexisting with a consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as one says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when one's consciousness approaches 1,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that seems to me the capacity of the human nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I say that is that subjectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,on January 10, 1965,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness that came on here was 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system was able to handle that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the miraculous event,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that which had been disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of power so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that the individual mind of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that had been called dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It never had another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It had no will of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one with the presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the presence that speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the presence that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,acts through the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which the world calls David,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but that is just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In theology and spiritual truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is called awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is also in English called Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,pure consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is called God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's beyond existence and nonexistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond truth and nontruth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is that out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself arose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is the absolute Godhead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond which there is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of the Godhead arose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you go into a divine space,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the divinity of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's divinity expressing itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from formlessness into form.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So God is therefore the creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not different than God,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the creator of all things visible and invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's beyond all things visible and invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Godhead out of which Godness arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked a lot about spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and theology and causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kitty wanted to be part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hear her meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in some other parts of the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out Kitty's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty's consciousness is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is very responsive to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's attuned to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the reason I wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,get Kitty in the picture is because
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we talk about consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody thinks we're talking about human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is vast,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes way beyond human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes within the physical domain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,up to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond a thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we go into other domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that's consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to talk about causality from a different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about causality from a Newtonian viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality within the Newtonian viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which goes up to about 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we talked about causality here in this tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about cause being on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.26,0:24:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the invisible realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the world we see is a world of effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is obvious when you're in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.96,0:24:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is still true when you're beyond 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.63,0:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you go beyond 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.72,0:24:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what you see is that time does not flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.72,0:24:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, in reality, with a capital R,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,time stands still.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a holographic universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.41,0:24:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:24:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is actually happening as you go beyond 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.68,0:25:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that this is a holographic universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.68,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in the universe sends off a vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.68,0:25:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The acupuncture system, the etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is like an antenna that both sends and receives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that there is an intersection of the vibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.84,0:25:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of the essence of all things radiating forth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.06,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in a standing hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.06,0:25:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what seems to,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.15,0:25:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the illusion that something is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.37,0:25:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.37,0:25:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in reality, nothing is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.37,0:25:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.37,0:25:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.69,0:25:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, there are no events.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.69,0:25:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.08,0:25:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what seems like motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when you walk through a hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.08,0:25:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as I walk around a hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.08,0:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.08,0:25:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, everybody's had the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at least in an art gallery,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.08,0:25:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you walk along and the eyes seem to follow you as you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:25:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, having a fixed level of motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a level of perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a function of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to fix one's perception to a given point,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as you move around the hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.64,0:26:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what seems to be events
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.77,0:26:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are really not events at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move around the hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.85,0:26:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.85,0:26:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, below the level of 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.92,0:26:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the level below 600 is the world of duality, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.92,0:26:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The world beyond 600
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.11,0:26:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is the world of non-duality, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.33,0:26:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.36,0:26:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as you move into a higher state of awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.36,0:26:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what you see is that all things are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.07,0:26:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, there is no here or there, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.07,0:26:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All things coexist simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.45,0:26:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere present, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.67,0:26:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.63,0:26:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the vibrations which exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.63,0:27:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which are registered by consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.17,0:27:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is not like a radio wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.17,0:27:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't, like, start here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought that I hold right this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.39,0:27:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is as it's held everywhere present
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.39,0:27:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the universe and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like on everywhere instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.46,0:27:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said in theology,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.94,0:27:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all hearts are open and all thoughts are known
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mind of God, resist, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.42,0:27:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a true signal, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.03,0:27:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.09,0:27:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.09,0:27:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is equivalent to the mind of God, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.38,0:27:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what people refer to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.70,0:27:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when they talk about the mind of God, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.76,0:27:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.76,0:27:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind of God goes beyond consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.76,0:28:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,onto the level of awareness, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.72,0:28:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Godhead beyond consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.70,0:28:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness is the Godhead, resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.02,0:28:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which consciousness arises, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.92,0:28:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're all antennas
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.92,0:28:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all vibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.92,0:28:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at a frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.92,0:28:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's instantly available
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,this would be a good way
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.92,0:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate with astronauts, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.30,0:28:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it would be a great way
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate with astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.30,0:28:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see logically on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.30,0:28:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you could know everything they're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling, saying what they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.39,0:28:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a grand way to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.39,0:28:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.87,0:28:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that's another practical thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When we said consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.12,0:28:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is far more than just human consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.70,0:28:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking about realms
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.12,0:29:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.12,0:29:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,religion calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.12,0:29:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,angelic, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.56,0:29:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 1,000 are the levels
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.56,0:29:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the angelic realms, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.10,0:29:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.10,0:29:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we saw that a lot of gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.10,0:29:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,get up to 740.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.10,0:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be stopping off points.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are critical spiritual gates
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which one goes through, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.32,0:29:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.76,0:29:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like large masses
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.76,0:29:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or smaller masses you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.24,0:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,reach certain levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.24,0:29:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's like a bunch of people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.76,0:29:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that stand outside a certain gate
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.76,0:29:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a critical spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.14,0:29:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to take place
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.14,0:29:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to get beyond the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The great block that I was concerned about
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.55,0:29:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the reasons I wrote the book
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.71,0:29:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was in our world, reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,reason seems to be the great blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people get beyond reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.00,0:30:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you push reason to its ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.00,0:30:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up at the level of genius, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.99,0:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,499 is the level that the world
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.99,0:30:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,considers genius, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.99,0:30:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people get beyond 499, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.31,0:30:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we said 0.4% of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.72,0:30:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,gets beyond 499, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.72,0:30:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so it's the great blockade, reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The opening of the heart then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.65,0:30:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,opens up love
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then 600 is the next big gate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,going from duality into non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.22,0:30:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I haven't really checked out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.22,0:30:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels from 700 on up,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but we noticed before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,when we were doing the tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that Maharaj, Nisargadatta Maharaj,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.68,0:31:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there seems to be a number of gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.00,0:31:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the low 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.13,0:31:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po, Huang Po calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.13,0:31:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,over 700, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.71,0:31:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,740, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.71,0:31:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,750, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.90,0:31:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,740, there seems to be another great gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.46,0:31:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,740 is the level of the mystic, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.79,0:31:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic has mastered
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.79,0:31:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual domain and our world, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has mastered also the physical world, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, to go through the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from 740 up to 800,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one has to maybe master both the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the physical, resist, simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.24,0:31:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.52,0:32:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there seems to be a great gap
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from 740 on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.61,0:32:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only go back on my own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.96,0:32:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a confrontation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.04,0:32:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,at 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.24,0:32:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At 800 is another gate, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.06,0:32:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At 800, one has to personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.57,0:32:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in quotes,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.76,0:32:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,face Lucifer himself, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.76,0:32:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To reach 850 means
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.63,0:32:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,one has what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Included within the domain of one's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.10,0:32:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness, consciousness, and mastery
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.10,0:32:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of Lucifer, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.10,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like one pulls up one's opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:33:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, what's the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.36,0:33:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of Lester Levinson, resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.74,0:33:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of Babaji, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.48,0:33:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a being that fell
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.29,0:33:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the confrontation with Lucifer, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.72,0:33:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fell before that, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.72,0:33:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never reached that level, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.18,0:33:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hit the mystic level,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.28,0:33:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,very often you leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very, very difficult to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.28,0:33:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you feel this enormous energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.66,0:33:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,flowing up your back, into your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:34:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system feels like it can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.19,0:34:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,like it handled too much voltage,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.02,0:34:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as though there's not enough insulation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.02,0:34:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,on the nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.62,0:34:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess many people just stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.71,0:34:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then for some reason, perhaps destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.40,0:34:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,some come back in and master the world
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as well, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a point at which suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.98,0:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a major confront
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with that which is Luciferic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.68,0:34:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is Luciferic is the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.16,0:34:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,through which the world calls gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.16,0:34:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,has to go through, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a point at which
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.67,0:34:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,not needing anything from anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.67,0:34:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,being complete and total and whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.66,0:34:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,one has enormous power over others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.66,0:35:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.17,0:35:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the temptation is to,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.32,0:35:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see where one could hold onto that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.18,0:35:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those are just interesting sidelights.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.18,0:35:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if everybody's really just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.18,0:35:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.18,0:35:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really wanted to share was that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.18,0:35:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, in this domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.18,0:35:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,goes up to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.18,0:35:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that are the angelic realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.18,0:35:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so evolution, we said evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.98,0:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,does not take place on the physical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.98,0:35:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.36,0:35:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes place on the level
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we call the angelic level, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.12,0:35:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Great beings who, once a being's energy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.11,0:35:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,surpasses one thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.11,0:35:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they no longer have a physical body, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.65,0:35:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body can't handle it, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.77,0:36:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.77,0:36:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we found out that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.38,0:36:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the body is an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.92,0:36:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.92,0:36:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.05,0:36:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you think or feel or do,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.05,0:36:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,every thought held in mind, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.53,0:36:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has an instant consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.53,0:36:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the entire universe, instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.53,0:36:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These vibrations intersect with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,creating a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.88,0:36:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This hologram, then, is experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.88,0:36:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on one's own level of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To move up the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.46,0:36:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,probably the most powerful tool is humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.46,0:36:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Most powerful tool is humility, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.07,0:36:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.19,0:36:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One is able to move up the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.19,0:36:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,unaided, on one's own hook, one might say, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.85,0:37:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One is able to move up the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,only by, with the help of the Holy Spirit, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.61,0:37:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Holy Spirit as reflected through angels, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.08,0:37:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher beings resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one cannot really do it unaided.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.60,0:37:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Scripture says.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.60,0:37:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It says one asks God,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.33,0:37:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever one holds in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.84,0:37:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as one's spiritual guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.97,0:37:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them with the evolution of their consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.97,0:37:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because without that, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.77,0:37:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And without humility, one would not ask for assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.31,0:37:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, humility seems to be the cornerstone
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.31,0:37:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,upon which all of this rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.37,0:37:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a lot of times in this tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.37,0:38:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for demonstration purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.37,0:38:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just try to get the range of something,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.37,0:38:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes I get a little different numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.76,0:38:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Horror vs. Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.79,0:38:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 840, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.27,0:38:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 855, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.58,0:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,853, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.58,0:38:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.50,0:38:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,850, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.50,0:38:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of this tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.08,0:38:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,video tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.11,0:38:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 840, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.11,0:38:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 852, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.36,0:38:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.94,0:38:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.52,0:38:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're trying to do is make the incomprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.52,0:38:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehensible and demonstrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.09,0:38:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the world of the mystic,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.67,0:38:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The world, once a person goes beyond 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.67,0:39:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality that they describe is difficult to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.62,0:39:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By using this map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.80,0:39:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and this whole presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.60,0:39:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is to create a context that is so inclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.88,0:39:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as logical and demonstrable,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.88,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that it makes understandable
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.59,0:39:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is ordinarily held to be not understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.59,0:39:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To make the incomprehensible comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.94,0:39:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is really what the purpose of it all is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.71,0:39:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to catch up on some of the things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.71,0:39:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that got passed over and maybe not explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.71,0:39:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That what, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.16,0:39:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what people consider tragedies in their life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.16,0:39:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are always opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.16,0:39:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The black night of the soul
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.51,0:40:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is the very springboard to letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.51,0:40:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is very tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it doesn't let go until
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all is the state of unbearable agony sets in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.02,0:40:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In my own experience, it was unbearable agony
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.98,0:40:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that finally made it let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.78,0:40:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the lives of the saints, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they talk about the black night of the soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.61,0:40:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that that is the opportunity to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.61,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of all one's positions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender completely to God, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.15,0:40:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.79,0:40:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a new experience of self and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.98,0:40:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,takes the place of the old.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.98,0:40:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though a new self is born
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and the old self has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.11,0:40:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from 500 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.36,0:40:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,have very specific effects in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.55,0:41:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we calibrated that at about the level of 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain releases endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.12,0:41:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The function of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.34,0:41:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in this whole field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.34,0:41:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make clear either.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.34,0:41:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain, it seems as though
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.24,0:41:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain is a receiving set
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.24,0:41:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy fields of consciousness then are like,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.27,0:41:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of like a radio wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.36,0:41:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain is like a receiver
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.36,0:41:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that picks up on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.36,0:41:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the same conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.78,0:41:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that was reached by Sir John Eccles,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.78,0:41:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a Nobel Prize winner in neurophysiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.88,0:41:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,who has written a whole series of books,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.13,0:41:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and those of you that are interested
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.13,0:41:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the scientific basis for this conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.13,0:41:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,can read Sir John Eccles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.93,0:41:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.70,0:41:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I thought the brain was run by
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.76,0:41:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,electrochemical events,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.76,0:42:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,electrical impulses and neurotransmitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.05,0:42:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all sustained,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sustained by the energy field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.24,0:42:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the power of the energy field of life itself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.31,0:42:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,transmitting through a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.31,0:42:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain is picking it up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.31,0:42:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,like a radio wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.88,0:42:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that a thought held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.88,0:42:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is very often picked up all across the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.88,0:42:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by a number of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of the thoughts that I've had
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.88,0:42:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and worked on, I'm sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.07,0:42:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,were just sitting there in the ether,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.07,0:42:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.07,0:42:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and picked up by a number of people simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.07,0:42:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and among them some people will act
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.07,0:42:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and others will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.07,0:42:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the consciousness that supports the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.71,0:42:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain then acts as a receiving set,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.71,0:42:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,much like a radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.71,0:42:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that the brain is picking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.99,0:42:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's really picking up a carrier wave
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.99,0:42:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,transmitted through the acupuncture system,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.01,0:43:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.24,0:43:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that the reason to avoid negative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.33,0:43:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is not because of the thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.52,0:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of the content,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.68,0:43:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of the musical notes themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.68,0:43:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of anything specific about it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.91,0:43:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,except the specific,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.91,0:43:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say, carrier wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.91,0:43:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So these levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.20,0:43:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say, are like carrier waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.32,0:43:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The content is not so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.39,0:43:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the energy field of the carrier wave itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.80,0:43:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We also said that 2.4% of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.80,0:43:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,are consistently negative in their responses,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.80,0:43:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and their responses are opposite to the normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.80,0:43:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Love makes them go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're repelled by love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.80,0:43:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And things that are negative and repulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.99,0:43:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are attractive to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.69,0:44:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This 2.4% is apparently the same people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.69,0:44:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that F. Scott Peck wrote about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.69,0:44:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in The People of the Lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.17,0:44:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What can be done about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.24,0:44:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't this latest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.24,0:44:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath a lot of the difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.45,0:44:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in emotional pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.64,0:44:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if you reflect on these levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.64,0:44:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.64,0:44:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,certain secrets will reveal themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.28,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of anger, resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.28,0:44:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of painful feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.38,0:44:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,humiliation, shame, disgrace, feeling victimized,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.38,0:44:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the energy of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.88,0:44:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.88,0:44:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when a person makes a mistake and feels humiliated,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.88,0:44:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes into shame, goes into a shame attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.95,0:44:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and feels guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.95,0:44:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what is all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.95,0:44:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be unhooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.78,0:44:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.78,0:44:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because underneath all of that is pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.78,0:45:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of pride by realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.78,0:45:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of humanness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.78,0:45:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you realize that mistakes are really
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.78,0:45:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.78,0:45:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not really your personal problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.94,0:45:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you let go of the pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.94,0:45:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then the chagrin, the humiliation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.94,0:45:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the resentment and all that disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.64,0:45:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of using kinesiology is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.64,0:45:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that you know what level you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.64,0:45:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never study a guru,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.80,0:45:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,never take a spiritual course,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.80,0:45:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,never follow a supposed master,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.93,0:45:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,until you know what level they're representing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.56,0:45:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That will solve one of the major problems
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.88,0:45:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual seekers,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.88,0:45:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is getting caught and trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.20,0:45:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in a negative spiritual field.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.20,0:45:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that everything is only true
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.46,0:45:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.91,0:45:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is only true.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.91,0:46:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that the world believes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.91,0:46:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer true
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.91,0:46:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at a higher level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.51,0:46:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing solves itself at the next level,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.51,0:46:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and what was the truth at one level
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.51,0:46:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes not a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.51,0:46:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.99,0:46:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So people let go of things
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.99,0:46:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that were once meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.99,0:46:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and caused a great deal of suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.99,0:46:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and move into a far more comfortable energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.16,0:46:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These differing levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.16,0:46:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so during the tape we've moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.16,0:46:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.16,0:46:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the subject of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.20,0:46:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First we looked at causality
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.39,0:46:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as it looks to people in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.39,0:46:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian level of A causes B causes C.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.39,0:46:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we looked at causality
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.87,0:46:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as it looks in the 500s,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.87,0:46:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where that which is held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.96,0:46:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,manifests sequentially in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.96,0:47:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality is not horizontal or linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.08,0:47:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but from the vertical,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.08,0:47:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's from the vertical to the lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.08,0:47:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we see manifestation and creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.08,0:47:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this again in the 600s,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.60,0:47:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we transcend that and we see
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.60,0:47:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's a holographic universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.60,0:47:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that nothing is really causing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.08,0:47:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,anything else at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.08,0:47:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 700s,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.17,0:47:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there is only is-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.78,0:47:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is already complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.78,0:47:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.10,0:47:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.10,0:47:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.10,0:47:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no separation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,between subject and object.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.55,0:47:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you move from duality to non-duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.55,0:47:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then there is no causality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.55,0:47:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is no creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.55,0:47:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because all is complete and total
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.55,0:47:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in its absolute perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.55,0:47:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In using the technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.02,0:48:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best to always look at one's motives
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.02,0:48:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll get the best answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.02,0:48:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if you yourself are coming from integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.02,0:48:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One has to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.53,0:48:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before you ask a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.53,0:48:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,can I handle the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.53,0:48:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and be honest about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.56,0:48:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps sometimes it's best
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.56,0:48:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave a certain question alone
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and return to it at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.72,0:48:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuitively, you'll sort of know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.72,0:48:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when is the right time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.72,0:48:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk a little bit about the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.33,0:48:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because most of the people who write
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.33,0:48:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for these videotapes are interested
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.64,0:48:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the subject matter of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.64,0:48:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the importance of the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.64,0:48:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it conveys an understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.64,0:48:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universe and of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.64,0:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and of causality and all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.00,0:48:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from a sort of comprehensive level.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.57,0:49:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose is really to help resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.73,0:49:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the problems of individuals and society.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.12,0:49:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe that the answers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.12,0:49:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to life's problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.12,0:49:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,both individually and collectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.37,0:49:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,arise out of an understanding of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.37,0:49:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only can advanced theoretical physics
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.56,0:49:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,not move any further than it is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.56,0:49:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,until it understands consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.66,0:49:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but mankind as a whole cannot really resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.66,0:49:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,any of its problems
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.66,0:49:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,unless it comes to grips with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.85,0:49:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the enormous influence and power
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.52,0:49:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.52,0:49:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked at the example
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.78,0:49:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the drug problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.78,0:49:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we saw that the position of the DEA
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the drug laws of the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.91,0:49:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.91,0:49:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,150 is a negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.29,0:49:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And we saw that an effective solution
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.29,0:50:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,would have to calibrate at 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.29,0:50:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So a knowledge of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.12,0:50:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all the subjects that we touched upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.34,0:50:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we barely touched upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.34,0:50:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in the field of archaeology,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.66,0:50:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,paleontology,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.66,0:50:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hope that study groups would form.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.66,0:50:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could spend, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.66,0:50:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,practically a whole lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just exploring archaeology,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.66,0:50:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,retracing history,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.66,0:50:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,recalibrating events in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.79,0:50:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,correcting errors
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.79,0:50:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and adding to man's knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.79,0:50:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at a very rapid rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.75,0:50:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So a crew of five or six people
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.75,0:50:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,who are very knowledgeable
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.75,0:50:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,about their particular field of endeavor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.75,0:50:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,would then know the right questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.88,0:50:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the subjects that we touched on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.00,0:50:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we did not pursue to any great depth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.06,0:50:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because it would take too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.06,0:51:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The book itself was done in order to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.00,0:51:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,express my own experience of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.96,0:51:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or knowledge of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.96,0:51:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and comprehension of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.00,0:51:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my own subjective, personal, spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.76,0:51:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then coming back into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.12,0:51:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to integrate it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.12,0:51:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with current scientific knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.34,0:51:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to put it into language
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.44,0:51:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and a conceptual format
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because ours is primarily a left-brain society
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.98,0:51:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in its approach to many subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.17,0:51:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea was to make
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.17,0:51:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is apparent to the mystic
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.17,0:51:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehensible to the left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.17,0:51:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that there would be a crossover
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.40,0:51:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.40,0:51:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of 850,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.58,0:51:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which was the level of the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.58,0:51:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the calibrated level of the sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.58,0:52:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Ken Wilber,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.58,0:52:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken Wilber's stratification
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of the perennial philosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.58,0:52:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,goes guru and then sage
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.61,0:52:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and he has these various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.87,0:52:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you look at a videotape
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or you listen to a lecturer,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.28,0:52:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you now have a tool
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.28,0:52:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which to discern
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.83,0:52:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is this the truth at all
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.83,0:52:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and so what level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.83,0:52:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is being reflected.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.63,0:52:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely view the videos
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.17,0:52:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and to merely read the book
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.17,0:52:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and think about it a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.17,0:52:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,has quite an advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.17,0:52:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to one's level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.17,0:52:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Each step that we take up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.52,0:52:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has enormous benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.52,0:52:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,very large figures
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.72,0:52:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in truth what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.77,0:52:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say a person moves
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.77,0:53:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,from consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.77,0:53:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,300 to 3.02.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.00,0:53:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very big jump
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.12,0:53:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will have an enormous impact
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.12,0:53:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on a person's life
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.25,0:53:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,logarithmic figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.25,0:53:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A move of even a few points
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.80,0:53:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,can make the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.80,0:53:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say being a worker
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.80,0:53:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,on the production line
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.80,0:53:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to jumping to foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.80,0:53:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few points makes the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,gives one the additional power
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.83,0:53:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that one needs to supervise others
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.83,0:53:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and be comfortable in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.83,0:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What spiritual techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.52,0:53:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what consciousness techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.52,0:53:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can one use to advance
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.52,0:53:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,one's consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.52,0:53:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about the understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.93,0:53:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of the nature of humanity itself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.93,0:53:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the compassion that arises
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.93,0:53:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.25,0:53:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a specific physical exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.25,0:53:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.25,0:54:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.25,0:54:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,about meditative techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.25,0:54:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and various things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that which is simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.70,0:54:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,very direct,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.70,0:54:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but which produces effects
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.89,0:54:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,due to persevering.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.40,0:54:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only necessary to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.40,0:54:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,one single spiritual concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.60,0:54:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All spiritual truth is contained
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.60,0:54:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in all other spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.60,0:54:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand and use one single tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.79,0:54:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.79,0:54:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times and all places
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.79,0:54:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to yourself and to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.79,0:54:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or compassion or willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.30,0:54:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or surrendering it to God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.30,0:54:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or letting go, wanting to change it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.30,0:54:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.00,0:54:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what one does is use this as a tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.00,0:54:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as a scalpel,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.00,0:54:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you persist with this one technique
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.45,0:54:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,relentlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.45,0:54:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time that there was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.00,0:55:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a great expansion of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.00,0:55:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.41,0:55:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own experience
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.41,0:55:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was the result of 11 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.41,0:55:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,11 days I fixedly
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.41,0:55:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,never allowed one single thought
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.41,0:55:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.60,0:55:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At first you start with thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.82,0:55:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that are practically paragraphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.82,0:55:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,whole stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.82,0:55:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let go of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.82,0:55:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of paragraphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.82,0:55:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of sentences,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of phrases,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.82,0:55:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you watch and you see
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.82,0:55:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts are beginning to arise
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.82,0:55:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you become aware of that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.49,0:55:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which is witnessing the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.49,0:55:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become the witness of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.72,0:55:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see that thoughts are arising
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.88,0:55:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from some kind of an energy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.88,0:55:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that wants to manifest as a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.88,0:55:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get back earlier and earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.91,0:55:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.91,0:55:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and so finally the mind falls silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.91,0:55:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and after 11 days of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.29,0:56:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly that already incredible state
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.81,0:56:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,expanded into its present,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.81,0:56:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.04,0:56:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the simplest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.98,0:56:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.98,0:56:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think one should just sit
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.07,0:56:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold out one's hands like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.61,0:56:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not to receive,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.28,0:56:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as many spiritual teachers will tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.28,0:56:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this is to receive the energy of God, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.28,0:56:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.67,0:56:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to sit like this
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.83,0:56:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and radiate out into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.44,0:56:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you will for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.44,0:56:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Very revealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.65,0:56:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit quietly someplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.00,0:56:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hold out one's hands thusly,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.00,0:56:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and express non-verbally
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.45,0:56:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is that you wish
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.77,0:57:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for the world and for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.77,0:57:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.48,0:57:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which humanity needs
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.08,0:57:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will reveal itself to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.08,0:57:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then that which intrinsically humanity is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.17,0:57:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals itself to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.17,0:57:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually that which is not
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.97,0:57:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real Self shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.97,0:57:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in all its radiance and splendor
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.97,0:57:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and magnificence and stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.97,0:57:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you see all things expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,their own essence in an absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.36,0:57:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,harmonious perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.36,0:57:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.74,0:57:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything already is as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.74,0:57:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no discontinuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.00,0:57:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is One.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.00,0:57:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is self-revealing,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.18,0:57:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is also
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.18,0:57:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,healing to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.88,0:57:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.88,0:57:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal the suffering of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.88,0:58:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and assuming this position
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.88,0:58:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically begins to reveal to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.01,0:58:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in a non-verbal way
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.36,0:58:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which jumps the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.36,0:58:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is the great block,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.55,0:58:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.55,0:58:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that isn't logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.55,0:58:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said it was logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.55,0:58:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,90% of the things you do
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.06,0:58:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,during the course of a day
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.06,0:58:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is not logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.06,0:58:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an automatic pattern recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.06,0:58:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and an automatic action.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.06,0:58:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego then takes credit for it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.06,0:58:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a split second after it occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.06,0:58:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and claims that it decided to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.06,0:58:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No such thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.06,0:58:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really watch how your mind operates,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.06,0:58:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that actually
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.60,0:58:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going on by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.60,0:58:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need a personal need to run it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.60,0:58:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One is just the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.76,0:58:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mind and its shenanigans
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the body and its
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.60,0:58:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,going here and going there,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.60,0:59:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which it does itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.60,0:59:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of like a karmic wind-up toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.60,0:59:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The body just runs itself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.60,0:59:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't really need a you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.60,0:59:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind runs itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.60,0:59:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It babbles on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.66,0:59:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need a you to run it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.30,0:59:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally comes the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.30,0:59:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.30,0:59:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which is something quite different
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.72,0:59:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,than the body and the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.72,0:59:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history that began
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.97,0:59:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when the person said to themself,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.36,0:59:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.36,0:59:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So when was I born?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.96,0:59:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born at age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.73,0:59:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly I became conscious of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.89,0:59:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that there was no consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.89,0:59:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.89,0:59:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly there was an awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.24,0:59:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and a consciousness of I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.24,0:59:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly there was the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.44,0:59:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that if one is,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.82,0:59:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there was the hypothetical possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.82,1:00:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember fear arising about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.74,1:00:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So with the birth of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.74,1:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,arises fear and the desire
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.74,1:00:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for continuation and survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.90,1:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the grace,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.37,1:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,by grace one transcends
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.37,1:00:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all these various levels
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.11,1:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and reaches the state of healing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.33,1:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and being healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.33,1:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that is the meditative practice
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.07,1:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I recommend when people say,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.07,1:00:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.29,1:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best meditative technique?
